'''Green Squad 3''' was one of eight [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] training squads who trained at [[Alliance Training Center-5/Green Squad]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ksift]]. They were previously known simply as [[Green Squad]], and helped in the defense of the base when [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces attacked just after they had retrieved the [[Datafile/Legends|data file]] [[Green3]] in their training exercises.

